{"tid":1992162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藥房狗真係無改錯名，望6月內地團重臨","createTime":"2020-04-28T03:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T11:05:15.000Z","uid":213877,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0ccde98ab927c27074a7a2261049e27f848e3300","tid":1992162,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"五一黃金周│土瓜灣藥房半黑營業省支出 留守老闆：似一鋪清袋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4396594/org/cd0a63dba34ecd840aa34cfb099d823a.jpg/81SXNUfYy9HL9td1PTkAuBkVrgHA6ZTWL1rAwy9awMM?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4396594%2Forg%2Fcd0a63dba34ecd840aa34cfb099d823a.jpg%2F81SXNUfYy9HL9td1PTkAuBkVrgHA6ZTWL1rAwy9awMM%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=34a129d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎下由內地入境香港須強制檢疫14日，持7人簽證的自由行旅客，今年五一黃金周變相無法來港。<br />\n九龍城碼頭、土瓜灣至紅磡一帶，一向為內地團聚集、用餐及購物重地，《香港01》記者上周六（25日）到現場視察，以往團體用餐的的酒樓大多已經暫停營業。有藥房只半開鐵閘繼續營業，老闆羅先生呆坐半日，進來購物的街坊不多，「嗰日好嘅，咪賣到十盒八盒口罩，點捱？好似一鋪清袋，仲要借銀行貼錢！」但數十萬貨品不能轉手、租金仍要交，加上希望伙計能繼續打拼，單獨一人繼續守住迎對黃金周。<span style=\"color: red;\">他樂觀說：「我點都等下啦，6月啦，大陸團陸續開啩！最多咪破產，有命就可能有希望。」</span>"},{"pid":"67ae0bd3de290f37f0d642092940642dffa3378c","tid":1992162,"uid":253016,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:36:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母藥房賤畜"},{"pid":"4eaa909c51f751a10ab79d88c94b799703651410","tid":1992162,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67ae0bd3de290f37f0d642092940642dffa3378c","tid":1992162,"uid":253016,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:36:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母藥房賤畜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5350d20de6fe026018751cdeb41343e5de548dc2","tid":1992162,"uid":258770,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"repl